blurb_text: The 2010 federal election was held on 21 August 2010. In Tasmania, the elected candidates were Helen Polley (Australian Labor Party), Eric Abetz (Liberal), Christine Milne (Australian Greens), Anne Urquhart (Australian Labor Party), Stephen Shane Parry (Liberal), and Lisa Singh (Australian Labor Party).
